<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Important_texts">Important texts</span></h2>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="The_Bible">The Bible</span></h3>
<p><i>The Bible is the holy text of Christians with the Old Testament written primarily in Hebrew and the New Testament in Greek.</i>
</p>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="English">English</span></h4>
<p><big><strong>
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Bible/King_James_Version" title="Bible/King James Version">King James Version (Authorized Version)</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bible/Douay-Rheims" title="Bible/Douay-Rheims">Douay-Rheims Version</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bible/Douay-Rheims,_The_Challoner_Revision" title="Bible/Douay-Rheims, The Challoner Revision">Douay-Rheims, The Challoner Revision</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bible/World_English_Bible" title="Bible/World English Bible">World English Bible (WEB)</a></li></ul>
<p></strong></big>
</p>
